    helpText: 'Regular self-assessment is crucial for identifying patterns, celebrating progress, and making necessary adjustments to your weight loss approach. Schedule a consistent weekly time to review your tracking data, noting what worked well and what challenged you, then make specific plans for improvement in the upcoming week. This structured reflection helps you stay accountable to your goals and prevents small setbacks from becoming major derailments by catching issues early and adjusting your strategy accordingly.'
