<parameter name="new_string">  {
    id: 'prompt-46',
    prompt: 'Schedule weekly progress check-ins with yourself by setting aside 30 minutes to review your food diary, weight trends, and exercise consistency',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Regular self-assessment is crucial for identifying patterns, celebrating progress, and making necessary adjustments to your weight loss approach. Schedule a consistent weekly time to review your tracking data, noting what worked well and what challenged you, then make specific plans for improvement in the upcoming week. This structured reflection helps you stay accountable to your goals and prevents small setbacks from becoming major derailments by catching issues early and adjusting your strategy accordingly.'
  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-47',
    prompt: 'Schedule and complete a 45-minute meal prep session to batch cook and portion 3 days worth of balanced dinners with measured portions',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Dedicated meal preparation removes the daily stress of dinner decisions and ensures you have portion-controlled, nutritious meals ready when you\'re tired or busy. Choose three balanced dinner recipes that can be made in larger quantities, then cook, portion, and store them in labeled containers with specific serving sizes. This proactive approach prevents ordering takeout or making impulsive food choices during hectic weekdays, keeping you consistently aligned with your weight loss goals.'
  }
];</parameter>
